Cryptex
=======

Cryptex is a fork of P4RS3LT0NGV3, a universal text encoder/decoder &
steganography tool. The upstream project's license (AGPL-3.0) and copyright
notices are preserved verbatim in LICENSE.

Fork maintained by Deepak Mistry (m4xx) — https://m4xx.cfd
Upstream: the P4RS3LT0NGV3 project (see git history for original commits).
